        <abstract> 
<p>CD much interested by ERL’s book [<hi rend="italic">On comparative longevity</hi> (1870)]. Is pleased to find ERL refers to CD’s "despised child" Pangenesis, and is also pleased how thoroughly ERL appreciates Herbert Spencer, a philosopher perhaps equal to any that has lived.</p> 
